// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3115 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bc385afb-6c45-5290-b229-af95bc276341

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
